latestPosts.caption:
What an absolute treat on our ongoing Ladakh Birding tour! We were thrilled to spot this magnificent Great Rosefinch and yes, it truly lives up to its name!💖 

It's called 'Great' not just for its stunning looks, but because 𝐢𝐭'𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐥𝐚𝐫𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐚𝐥𝐥 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐫𝐨𝐬𝐞𝐟𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐬 𝐢𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐰𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝! 

You'll find these beauties foraging for seeds in the challenging, sparse terrains above the tree line in summers. 

Travel Ladakh with @quantumexplorerinc
